title: Master Software Services Agreement
meta: | type: contract | ref: MSA-2025-04 | date: 2025-04-01

section: 1. Definitions
def: Services | meaning: Cloud hosting, managed support, and integration work described in a Statement of Work.
def: SOW | meaning: A written Statement of Work executed under this Agreement.
def: Confidential Information | meaning: Non-public information disclosed by either Party marked or reasonably understood as confidential.

section: 2. Parties
contact: Helix Cloud Systems, Inc. | role: Provider | email: legal@helix.com
contact: Brightwave Retail Ltd. | role: Customer | email: ops@brightwave.com

section: 3. Scope
text: Provider will deliver the Services described in each SOW in accordance with this Agreement.

section: 4. Terms
clause: Order of precedence | scope: Contract | text: This Agreement prevails over any SOW.
clause: Change management | scope: Contract | text: Changes to a SOW require written approval by both Parties.
obligation: Maintain uptime | owner: Provider | by: 2025-12-31
obligation: Provide TAM | owner: Provider | by: 2025-04-15
warranty: Performance | owner: Provider | period: 12 months
sla: Monthly uptime | target: 99.9% | priority: P1
clause: Intellectual Property | scope: IP | text: Provider retains rights to pre-existing tools.
clause: Confidentiality | scope: Contract | period: 3 years
clause: Governing Law | scope: Legal | jurisdiction: New York

section: 5. Execution
route: sequential
require: legal
require: cfo
approve: Legal review | by: Priya Anand | role: legal | at: 2025-04-01
approve: CFO signoff | by: Marcus Hale | role: cfo | at: 2025-04-01